Hands-on experience with semantic layers, data modeling, and analytics platforms;
Knowledge of Generative AI, prompt engineering, and RAG architectures;
Experience with causal inference techniques and data-driven experimentation will be valued;
Proactivity and dynamism;
Organizational and communication skills.


